                :XMLProcessor ;
       rdfs:comment "XML database and XQuery processor"@en ;
       rdfs:label "BaseX"@en ;
       <http://xmlns.com/foaf/0.1/isPrimaryTopicOf> <https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BaseX> .


###  http://www.softlang.org/ontologies/te#Bison
:Bison rdf:type owl:NamedIndividual ,
